rawContent:
What’s #depression? 

I drink ice water in tumblers with lids. After draining one, I opened it to refill it and saw a cockroach embedded in a piece of ice. Removed that piece, refilled it, and took a sip- didn’t even chuck the rest of the ice. 

It’s identifying as the roach.
